WEBVTT

00:03:29.638 --> 00:03:32.947
And they're like, "OK dude,
I don't know why you're getting so upset,

00:03:32.971 --> 00:03:34.506
I want to make a phone call.

00:03:34.530 --> 00:03:37.017
I'm going to give it back to you
as soon as I'm done.

00:03:37.041 --> 00:03:38.191
Whatever."

00:03:39.140 --> 00:03:43.102
And then imagine if someone takes
that cell phone out of your hands --

00:03:43.126 --> 00:03:45.519
I don't know -- once a day,

00:03:46.438 --> 00:03:47.596
twice a day,

00:03:47.620 --> 00:03:48.898
random times.

00:03:49.427 --> 00:03:50.578
And the explanation is,

00:03:50.602 --> 00:03:54.412
"Yeah, well, I mean,
you got a fancy case,"

00:03:54.436 --> 00:03:58.124
or "You shouldn't have
taken it out of your pocket,"

00:03:58.148 --> 00:04:00.413
or "Yep. Yeah.